title: File your confirmation statement (annual return) with Companies House

heading_context: File your confirmation statement (annual return) with Companies House
chunks.html_content:
Use this service to:

  • file your confirmation statement (previously annual return)
  • sign up for email alerts to let you know when your confirmation statement is due

heading_context: File your confirmation statement (annual return) with Companies House
chunks.html_content:
Read guidance on preparing your confirmation statement

You’ll need a Companies House password and authentication code.

If you do not have these, you can register online.
